Path: godot/classes/class_callable.rst
Summary: Describes the equality and inequality operators for Callable objects.

Operator Descriptions

Method: operator !=(right: Callable) -> bool
Returns `true` if both Callable objects invoke different targets.

Method: operator ==(right: Callable) -> bool
Returns `true` if both Callable objects invoke the same custom target.